thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F902173%2Fxlarge%2F7fecfeb0dd4e12266522acb83575fa8a.jpg&h=f9e7f668&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n本劇主要描寫主人翁「大門未知子」，是一位外型和一般醫生形象截然不同的神秘女子，因為日本特殊的醫院文化，衍生出派遣醫生這樣的工作形式，她從醫大畢業後就到惡劣環境行醫練出了一身精湛的開刀技術，但她的表現近乎不通人情，時間一到就立刻下班，她在醫院從不參與派系鬥爭，與大學醫院醫局人員間的糾葛，僅以她最擅長的開刀技術在這樣的體系下生存，成為醫院裡醫生的眼中釘<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=0bD1wHgmdXnszu8A5afz7%2F1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=c3468d87\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=0bD1wHgmdXnszu8A5afz7%2F1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=757ff73a\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72bda5287e8fdc182ee20c7f9a26900d3a6f9305","tid":520481,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T13:23:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b6ced5e129d9d59049318d6ef58fe2436584886","tid":520481,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T10:08:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89a91f9d61e8c0882056bb017fdf670d59950340","tid":520481,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T10:32:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\